title: Hour 3 - The Dream Man Cave
itunes:title: Hour 3 - The Dream Man Cave
description:
Covino & Rich are filling in for Dan Patrick and finish discussing Aaron Rodger’s first tattoo. They talk Covino’s childhood dream – a sweet man cave! Rich is a dream killer and you’ll find out the real reason why. Plus, the fellas talk Tommy Fury/FIGHTS and dedication to your favorite team.
